===Noun===
'''ruck'''

# a [[crowd]], [[throng]] or [[multitude]] of people
#(''Rugby'') the situation formed when a [[runner]] is brought to [[ground]] and one or more members of each side are enagaged above the [[ball]], trying to win [[possession]] of it; a [[loose scrum]]
